{"section": "Exercise 2.22.2: Deducing the key from a single (plaintext, ciphertext) pair.", "qid": 0, "instructions": "<div class=\"activity-instructions\">\n <p>\n  In the questions below, let N = 79 and k = 43. Use the simple cryptosystem defined above.\n </p>\n</div>\n", "question": "<div class=\"question\">\n <div class=\"setup flex-row\">\n  <div class=\"label\">\n   3)\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   Decrypt the ciphertext c = 12.\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"question-container flex-row\">\n  <div class=\"input\">\n   <pre><!----><textarea class=\"zb-text-area hide-scrollbar ember-text-area ember-view\" cols=\"20\" id=\"ember155\" rows=\"1\" spellcheck=\"false\"></textarea><!----></pre>\n   <div class=\"buttons flex-row\">\n    <button class=\"check-button zb-button primary raised ember-view\" id=\"ember156\">\n     <!-- -->\n     <span class=\"title\">\n      Check\n     </span>\n    </button>\n    <button class=\"show-answer-button zb-button secondary ember-view\" id=\"ember157\" style=\"\">\n     <!-- -->\n     <span class=\"title\">\n      Show answer\n     </span>\n    </button>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n</div>\n", "choices": [], "answer": "<div class=\"answer\">\n <p>\n  If c = (m + k) mod N, then k = (c - m) mod N\n  <br/>\n  <br/>\n  k = (1322 - 3411) mod 4657 = -2089 mod 4657 = 2568\n </p>\n</div>\n", "explanation": null}